WEBVTT

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:56.099
Buying a chicken.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.420
This one doesn't look right.

00:02:03.359 --> 00:02:04.140
This one's no good either.

00:02:04.799 --> 00:02:05.719
What do you mean, look right?

00:02:06.260 --> 00:02:08.039
You pick a chicken by vibes now?

00:02:08.219 --> 00:02:09.219
Well, of course.

00:02:09.580 --> 00:02:10.500
Gotta look carefully.

00:02:16.479 --> 00:02:17.520
This one feels right.

00:02:18.099 --> 00:02:18.620
I'll take it.

00:02:19.099 --> 00:02:19.860
This one works.

00:02:20.419 --> 00:02:20.979
That's the one.

00:02:21.139 --> 00:02:21.819
I'll give it to you cheap.

00:02:22.039 --> 00:02:22.620
Man...

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.520
They all look exactly the same.

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:45.120
Everyone's here today

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:46.599
To bear witness for us

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:49.219
You've all made up your minds, right?

00:02:50.759 --> 00:02:51.659
Then let's get started

00:03:18.419 --> 00:03:19.080
This time

00:03:19.919 --> 00:03:20.719
That should be enough, right?

00:03:21.139 --> 00:03:22.659
Can we talk business now?

00:03:22.939 --> 00:03:23.439
Sure.

00:03:24.180 --> 00:03:25.039
Let's get into the details.

00:03:40.740 --> 00:03:41.740
Take a break.

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.400
You're overthinking it.

00:03:45.039 --> 00:03:45.659
My head hurts.

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:15.560
Dad.

00:04:17.160 --> 00:04:17.939
How can a person

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:19.379
Change so suddenly?

00:04:23.319 --> 00:04:24.740
Change on a whim?

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:27.120
That'd make them a chameleon.

00:04:28.459 --> 00:04:28.899
Exactly.

00:04:29.959 --> 00:04:31.100
Just like a chameleon.

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:34.879
On a tree, it turns the tree's color.

00:04:36.300 --> 00:04:37.180
On a leaf,

00:04:37.220 --> 00:04:38.639
It turns the leaf's color.

00:04:39.899 --> 00:04:41.519
It blends into the environment

00:04:41.579 --> 00:04:42.459
To protect itself.

00:04:43.899 --> 00:04:45.319
Doesn't seem wrong to me.

00:04:47.819 --> 00:04:48.560
Look,

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:52.240
Insects have their own logic,

00:04:53.259 --> 00:04:55.500
And birds have theirs.

00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:58.939
Put a bug and a bird together,

00:04:59.740 --> 00:05:01.060
How can they reason with each other?

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:03.079
So two people with different views

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.660
Can't ever be together?

00:05:07.420 --> 00:05:09.100
One side always has to change?

00:05:10.459 --> 00:05:12.600
Change isn't a bad thing.

00:05:13.819 --> 00:05:15.240
You can't become a chameleon

00:05:16.199 --> 00:05:18.339
Because you aren't one.

00:05:19.899 --> 00:05:20.560
Look,

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:23.100
From your angle,

00:05:23.379 --> 00:05:24.300
Looking at this mountain,

00:05:25.199 --> 00:05:26.399
Hasn't it stayed the same

00:05:26.660 --> 00:05:27.759
For decades?

00:05:28.879 --> 00:05:29.579
But actually,

00:05:29.899 --> 00:05:32.199
It's changing every single day.

00:05:33.060 --> 00:05:34.819
Today it bears a fruit,

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:37.480
Tomorrow it grows some grass.

00:05:38.540 --> 00:05:40.779
It's changing according to

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:41.959
Its own will.

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:44.279
But then again,

00:05:44.819 --> 00:05:46.379
If the mountain has no trees,

00:05:47.100 --> 00:05:48.360
No grass,

00:05:49.019 --> 00:05:50.339
No animals,

00:05:50.740 --> 00:05:53.139
And turns into a bare, barren hill,

00:05:54.699 --> 00:05:56.160
Would it be happy about that?

00:05:59.879 --> 00:06:01.500
If someone wants you

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:02.540
To become someone

00:06:02.540 --> 00:06:04.180
Even you yourself don't like,

00:06:04.699 --> 00:06:05.839
It's not necessarily good for you.

00:06:07.180 --> 00:06:07.800
But

00:06:08.819 --> 00:06:10.319
It's definitely good for him.

00:06:27.339 --> 00:06:28.079
Kiddo

00:06:29.079 --> 00:06:30.939
If you've got anything weighing on you,

00:06:31.699 --> 00:06:33.339
Just shout it at the mountain.

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:35.800
Bottling it all up inside,

00:06:36.339 --> 00:06:37.459
Won't that just make it worse?

00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:16.639
Attention, villagers

00:07:16.779 --> 00:07:18.360
Listen up

00:07:19.019 --> 00:07:20.040
A while back

00:07:20.399 --> 00:07:21.339
The circus

00:07:21.720 --> 00:07:24.120
Had an accident near our village

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:26.300
And one of the monkeys ran off

00:07:26.639 --> 00:07:27.540
Now

00:07:27.860 --> 00:07:29.779
There's a public reward

00:07:30.139 --> 00:07:32.620
Anyone with useful information

00:07:32.879 --> 00:07:34.519
Will get a reward

00:07:35.180 --> 00:07:37.560
Everyone gets a reward

00:07:40.339 --> 00:07:41.420
That monkey belongs

00:07:41.420 --> 00:07:42.579
In the mountains

00:07:42.779 --> 00:07:44.819
Caught by the circus for people's amusement

00:07:46.220 --> 00:07:47.060
That's just awful

00:07:48.819 --> 00:07:49.759
Actually,

00:07:49.839 --> 00:07:51.819
Animals understand feelings too

00:07:52.459 --> 00:07:53.939
If you treat it well

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:55.420
Why would it ever run away?

00:07:56.959 --> 00:07:57.800
Think about it

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:00.000
Locked in a cage every day

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:02.660
Beaten, yelled at

00:08:02.819 --> 00:08:04.920
Trained, forced to perform

00:08:05.279 --> 00:08:07.019
Of course it would run away

00:08:08.259 --> 00:08:09.339
I'm telling you

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.120
Maybe

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:14.500
If that accident hadn't happened

00:08:21.040 --> 00:08:22.079
Dad, you're right.

00:08:23.220 --> 00:08:24.939
That probably wasn't a car accident at all.

00:08:25.540 --> 00:08:26.300
It was them.

00:08:26.300 --> 00:08:27.620
A jailbreak they'd been planning for ages.

00:08:27.899 --> 00:08:28.939
Think about it.

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:30.920
Those little monkeys ran off into the mountains.

00:08:31.079 --> 00:08:32.039
How happy they must be!

00:08:32.379 --> 00:08:33.600
How joyful!

00:08:33.899 --> 00:08:35.559
They're free.

00:08:35.860 --> 00:08:37.379
And there are all sorts of

00:08:37.379 --> 00:08:38.820
Different lifestyles.

00:08:40.299 --> 00:08:41.039
Right.

00:08:42.340 --> 00:08:43.740
Some are willing to stay caged up,

00:08:43.799 --> 00:08:44.940
So they stay in the cage.

00:08:45.679 --> 00:08:46.519
Some want to escape,

00:08:46.559 --> 00:08:47.460
So they escape.

00:08:48.179 --> 00:08:49.259
To each their own way of living.

00:08:49.379 --> 00:08:50.139
Exactly.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:55.960
What are you doing?

00:08:56.179 --> 00:08:56.919
Jailbreak.

00:08:59.220 --> 00:09:01.019
The bride price doesn't include the three golds.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:04.039
Gold necklace, gold ring, gold bracelet.

00:09:04.379 --> 00:09:05.960
You have to go to the county town to buy them.

00:09:06.659 --> 00:09:08.259
Let our Xiaofang pick them out herself.

00:09:10.100 --> 00:09:10.860
Pick them herself.

00:09:10.899 --> 00:09:11.960
Buy whatever she wants.

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:13.179
How can that work?

00:09:13.299 --> 00:09:14.919
There's gotta be a limit, right?

00:09:16.580 --> 00:09:17.120
How about this.

00:09:18.340 --> 00:09:20.320
For the three golds, we'll pay 5,000.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:22.980
What can 5,000 even buy?

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:24.879
Everyone listen to me.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:27.059
Today is the last day, you know.

00:09:27.220 --> 00:09:28.360
If we can't settle it today,

00:09:28.519 --> 00:09:29.639
The village won't get involved anymore.

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:30.399
Whatever you two want to do,

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:31.179
You're on your own.

00:09:31.559 --> 00:09:32.259
Fine.

00:09:32.879 --> 00:09:34.059
5,000 it is.

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:35.519
Then let's agree on this.

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:36.159
The wedding banquet

00:09:36.379 --> 00:09:37.600
Has to be held in the county town.

00:09:38.039 --> 00:09:38.720
At least

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:40.259
20 tables.

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.139
No problem.

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:44.279
So the wedding gift money we collect

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:45.940
Gets split evenly between our families.

00:09:46.019 --> 00:09:46.940
No way.

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:47.799
No way.

00:09:48.259 --> 00:09:48.740
Then how about this.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:51.519
You get 60, we get 40.

00:09:51.580 --> 00:09:52.519
We take the loss. Deal?

00:09:52.779 --> 00:09:54.139
We get 70, you get 30.

00:09:54.519 --> 00:09:55.059
20-80.

00:09:55.700 --> 00:09:56.220
No way.

00:09:56.419 --> 00:09:57.179
40-60.

00:09:57.259 --> 00:09:58.080
Final offer: 70-30.

00:09:58.659 --> 00:09:59.220
70-30.

00:10:00.019 --> 00:10:00.720
Xiaofang.

00:10:00.879 --> 00:10:02.120
I heard that cheapskate Qi family

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:03.179
Finally coughed up some cash.

00:10:03.279 --> 00:10:03.940
Yeah.

00:10:04.019 --> 00:10:05.679
The money's pretty much settled.

00:10:06.659 --> 00:10:07.519
Xiaofang.

00:10:07.740 --> 00:10:08.940
Now you can relax.

00:10:09.259 --> 00:10:10.340
Since you're pregnant,

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:11.440
You've got to get married.

00:10:11.600 --> 00:10:13.419
Once you're married, no one will gossip.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.120
Right.

00:10:14.159 --> 00:10:15.419
With a big belly and no wedding,

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.080
Your family gets anxious too, right?

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:19.539
We're all just worried for you.

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:20.320
Xiaofang.

00:10:20.679 --> 00:10:22.639
We'll be waiting to drink at your wedding.

00:10:22.740 --> 00:10:23.120
Okay.

00:10:23.460 --> 00:10:24.419
Thank you, Auntie.

00:10:33.980 --> 00:10:34.820
This isn't just about

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:35.659
You and Qi Xiaowei

00:10:35.700 --> 00:10:36.519
Being lovey-dovey anymore.

00:10:36.659 --> 00:10:38.860
It's a war between two families.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:47.340
What decent girl would ever

00:10:47.379 --> 00:10:48.720
Strip naked and let someone paint her?

00:10:48.820 --> 00:10:50.039
Who'd dare marry a girl like that?

00:10:50.279 --> 00:10:50.820
Who'd dare?

00:10:55.419 --> 00:10:56.100
If she hadn't that day

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.279
Kissed me and all that stuff,

00:10:57.419 --> 00:10:58.399
I never would've been able to paint it.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.399
I don't want people

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:00.419
Treating me like an idiot anymore,

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:01.620
Pointing fingers behind my back,

00:11:01.659 --> 00:11:02.799
Gossiping about me.

00:11:15.100 --> 00:11:15.639
Xiaofang

00:11:17.179 --> 00:11:17.720
That temper of yours,

00:11:17.720 --> 00:11:18.759
Can you ever change it?

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:23.220
Hello, everyone.

00:11:24.279 --> 00:11:25.559
I'm Yang Xiaofang.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:26.460
Seventy-thirty, final offer.

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:27.120
Stop arguing!

00:11:27.919 --> 00:11:28.419
Listen.

00:11:28.860 --> 00:11:29.919
I have something to say.

00:11:34.419 --> 00:11:35.840
Aunties of the village,

00:11:35.879 --> 00:11:37.360
Please stop worrying about me.

00:11:38.360 --> 00:11:39.080
Aunt, Second Aunt,

00:11:39.100 --> 00:11:40.299
You don't need to bother either.

00:11:40.820 --> 00:11:42.759
I don't want Qi Xiaowei's bride price.

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:44.539
I'm not marrying him.

00:11:46.179 --> 00:11:47.419
I, Yang Xiaofang,

00:11:47.580 --> 00:11:49.279
I don't love Qi Xiaowei anymore.

00:11:49.500 --> 00:11:50.779
So I'm not marrying him.

00:11:52.059 --> 00:11:54.259
I'll always stay true to my choices.

00:11:54.620 --> 00:11:56.240
I do whatever I think is right.

00:11:57.220 --> 00:11:58.820
I, Yang Xiaofang,

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:01.480
Don't love Qi Xiaowei anymore.

00:12:02.220 --> 00:12:05.179
I'm not marrying him.

00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:16.299
Not marrying him!

00:12:19.759 --> 00:12:21.679
I don't want Qi Xiaowei's bride price.

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:24.320
I'm not marrying him.

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:26.620
I, Yang Xiaofang,

00:12:27.159 --> 00:12:28.399
Don't love Qi Xiaowei anymore.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.559
So I'm not marrying him.

00:12:35.340 --> 00:12:36.639
I, Yang Xiaofang,

00:12:37.159 --> 00:12:38.779
I don't love Qi Xiaowei anymore.

00:12:39.779 --> 00:12:41.279
I'm not marrying him.

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:50.740
I'm not marrying him!

00:13:08.340 --> 00:13:09.379
What did she say?

00:13:09.980 --> 00:13:11.159
I couldn't hear clearly.

00:13:11.340 --> 00:13:12.279
Xiaofang said

00:13:12.460 --> 00:13:14.559
She doesn't want Qi Xiaowei's bride price.

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:16.679
And she's not marrying him either.

00:13:17.019 --> 00:13:17.620
Right.

00:13:19.639 --> 00:13:21.000
This girl Xiaofang

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:22.120
Really takes after Xia.

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:23.299
That spunk you had back then,

00:13:24.879 --> 00:13:25.419
It's amusing.

00:13:26.159 --> 00:13:27.059
Grandma,

00:13:27.399 --> 00:13:29.620
You weren't bad yourself back then.

00:13:29.820 --> 00:13:30.299
You...

00:13:31.340 --> 00:13:32.240
Manxia,

00:13:32.460 --> 00:13:33.419
That granddaughter of yours

00:13:33.500 --> 00:13:34.639
Sure knows how to mess around.

00:13:34.840 --> 00:13:35.879
What do you mean, mess around?

00:13:36.019 --> 00:13:38.539
If anyone talks about my granddaughter again,

00:13:39.100 --> 00:13:40.820
I'll dig up the old dirt.

00:13:41.059 --> 00:13:43.059
All your youthful shenanigans,

00:13:44.039 --> 00:13:45.460
I'll spill every one of them.

00:13:47.759 --> 00:13:49.100
That'd be quite a show.

00:13:51.299 --> 00:13:51.980
Xiaofang,

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:53.460
You're not marrying Qi Xiaowei anymore?

00:13:53.820 --> 00:13:54.460
Not marrying him.

00:13:55.100 --> 00:13:55.379
If you don't marry him,

00:13:55.419 --> 00:13:56.620
Would Qi Xiaowei even agree?

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.100
So what if he doesn't?

00:13:58.320 --> 00:13:59.620
With what his family pulled,

00:13:59.639 --> 00:14:00.360
If I were Xiaofang,

00:14:00.360 --> 00:14:01.320
I'd have snapped long ago.

00:14:01.659 --> 00:14:02.100
Xiaofang,

00:14:02.220 --> 00:14:03.220
If you need any help,

00:14:03.220 --> 00:14:04.039
Just tell Auntie, okay?

00:14:04.139 --> 00:14:05.879
Take it easy, you're pregnant.

00:14:06.220 --> 00:14:07.080
Okay.

00:14:15.139 --> 00:14:15.779
Yang Xiaofang,

00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:17.419
What's that supposed to mean?

00:14:19.379 --> 00:14:20.120
Hey, I'm talking to you.

00:14:20.139 --> 00:14:21.000
What are you trying to do?

00:14:25.519 --> 00:14:26.919
Didn't you hear it all?

00:14:27.779 --> 00:14:28.860
I don't want the bride price.

00:14:28.940 --> 00:14:29.779
I'm not marrying you.

00:14:29.820 --> 00:14:30.639
We're breaking up.

00:14:31.779 --> 00:14:32.860
You're pregnant, and you...

00:14:33.159 --> 00:14:34.600
You're just breaking up, just like that?

00:14:34.620 --> 00:14:35.740
You think this is playing house?

00:14:35.799 --> 00:14:37.460
I put in so much effort,

00:14:37.500 --> 00:14:38.419
Finally getting the money situation

00:14:38.419 --> 00:14:39.220
All sorted out.

00:14:39.279 --> 00:14:39.799
And you?

00:14:39.799 --> 00:14:40.799
You grab a megaphone

00:14:40.840 --> 00:14:41.720
And shout it at everyone,

00:14:41.919 --> 00:14:43.279
Letting the whole world know.

00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:44.740
Ever since you came back,

00:14:44.759 --> 00:14:46.139
How much trouble have you stirred up?

00:14:46.159 --> 00:14:47.200
What on earth do you want?

00:14:50.779 --> 00:14:51.340
Qi Xiaowei,

00:14:52.059 --> 00:14:53.100
If I hadn't done this,

00:14:53.120 --> 00:14:53.799
I don't know how long my Aunt

00:14:53.799 --> 00:14:54.340
Would keep bickering

00:14:54.340 --> 00:14:55.480
With your parents.

00:14:56.120 --> 00:14:56.919
How many times have I said

00:14:56.940 --> 00:14:57.899
This is between the two of us?

00:14:57.960 --> 00:14:59.500
And so many people got dragged in.

00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:01.340
This way it's settled.

00:15:01.559 --> 00:15:02.600
Now they can finally shut up, right?

00:15:03.919 --> 00:15:04.460
From now on,

00:15:04.460 --> 00:15:05.620
You don't need to sweet-talk me.

00:15:06.179 --> 00:15:07.379
And I, Yang Xiaofang, will never

00:15:07.379 --> 00:15:08.340
Embarrass you again.

00:15:08.899 --> 00:15:10.500
The road's wide, we each go our own way.

00:15:10.879 --> 00:15:12.019
I'm not joking with you.

00:15:12.580 --> 00:15:13.220
I don't love you anymore.

00:15:13.259 --> 00:15:14.039
We're breaking up.

00:15:15.559 --> 00:15:17.059
Look, so many people got involved,

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:19.759
I had no other choice.

00:15:20.139 --> 00:15:21.139
What gives you the right to say you don't love me

00:15:21.179 --> 00:15:21.879
And just stop loving me?

00:15:26.039 --> 00:15:27.320
If you can flip on a dime,

00:15:27.639 --> 00:15:28.379
Why can't I?

00:15:28.379 --> 00:15:29.460
Say I don't love you, and I don't.

00:15:31.820 --> 00:15:32.559
I don't agree.

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:34.639
Yang Xiaofang,

00:15:35.419 --> 00:15:36.419
You're pregnant.

00:15:36.759 --> 00:15:37.759
If you don't marry me,

00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:38.779
Who else are you going to find?

00:15:38.840 --> 00:15:39.720
Who would even want you?

00:15:45.379 --> 00:15:46.019
You hit me?

00:15:46.259 --> 00:15:47.240
That one's from him.

00:15:51.179 --> 00:15:52.059
And this one's from me.

00:16:04.580 --> 00:16:06.940
Aunt, have some sweet drink.

00:16:10.500 --> 00:16:12.399
Who upset our Aunt?

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:16.039
I don't want it.

00:16:17.340 --> 00:16:18.620
Playing dumb when you know full well.

00:16:21.440 --> 00:16:23.360
The 188,000 amount

00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:24.279
Was all settled.

00:16:24.759 --> 00:16:26.120
One shout of yours on the loudspeaker

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:27.159
And it's all off.

00:16:27.700 --> 00:16:28.860
I don't love Qi Xiaowei anymore.

00:16:28.899 --> 00:16:30.159
Of course I can't marry him.

00:16:31.200 --> 00:16:32.779
You were the one madly in love,

00:16:32.799 --> 00:16:33.539
And in the blink of an eye,

00:16:33.580 --> 00:16:34.320
You say you don't love him.

00:16:34.519 --> 00:16:35.659
I don't care whether you love him now.

00:16:35.899 --> 00:16:36.620
You tell me,

00:16:36.879 --> 00:16:37.659
What are we going to do?

00:16:37.940 --> 00:16:38.779
What do you mean, what to do?

00:16:38.899 --> 00:16:39.899
Haven't I already taken care of it?

00:16:40.220 --> 00:16:41.299
What do you mean, taken care of?

00:16:42.299 --> 00:16:43.639
You don't want the baby in your belly?

00:16:44.860 --> 00:16:45.940
You're not planning to stay

00:16:45.940 --> 00:16:46.799
In the village anymore?

00:16:47.039 --> 00:16:48.480
You just flap your lips

00:16:48.539 --> 00:16:49.279
And say you're not marrying him.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.940
How are we supposed to explain this to people?

00:16:51.399 --> 00:16:52.740
Explain what?

00:16:53.259 --> 00:16:54.440
Me not marrying Qi Xiaowei,

00:16:54.440 --> 00:16:55.419
Does the earth shake?

00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:56.779
Ridiculous.

00:16:56.899 --> 00:16:58.379
Earth doesn't move, mountains don't shake.

00:16:58.840 --> 00:17:00.840
But the baby in your belly can't wait!

00:17:01.399 --> 00:17:02.120
Xiaofang,

00:17:02.460 --> 00:17:04.140
Being willful won't put food on the table.

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:06.039
I'm not being willful.

00:17:06.259 --> 00:17:07.200
I support being willful.

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:09.079
Fang, Uncle supports you.

00:17:10.779 --> 00:17:11.359
What happened?

00:17:11.539 --> 00:17:12.980
I almost went down the wrong path.

00:17:12.980 --> 00:17:13.920
Thanks to what you shouted just now.

00:17:13.920 --> 00:17:14.700
What happened to you?

00:17:14.779 --> 00:17:15.799
It's nothing, I just took a fall.

00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:17.119
I back your willfulness.

00:17:17.380 --> 00:17:18.619
I'm not being willful.

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:20.640
You're the most willful one.

00:17:21.220 --> 00:17:22.740
Almost 40 and still tripping while walking?

00:17:23.619 --> 00:17:24.859
The whole family scrimped and saved

00:17:24.900 --> 00:17:25.700
To put you through college,

00:17:25.740 --> 00:17:26.920
All counting on you to amount to something.

00:17:27.619 --> 00:17:28.359
Those classmates of yours,

00:17:28.539 --> 00:17:29.920
Built houses in the village, married in the county,

00:17:30.039 --> 00:17:31.440
Got cars, houses, a future.

00:17:31.500 --> 00:17:31.960
What have you got?

00:17:32.079 --> 00:17:33.279
I've got ideals. What do I have?

00:17:33.279 --> 00:17:33.900
Ideals, my foot!

00:17:33.960 --> 00:17:35.779
Go get lost in your room and think about it!

00:17:35.859 --> 00:17:36.480
Ideals!

00:17:37.519 --> 00:17:38.859
What are you yelling for?

00:17:39.279 --> 00:17:42.059
You're gonna bring the roof down.

00:17:43.299 --> 00:17:43.859
Damn it.

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:47.059
That Qi family is outrageous.

00:17:47.359 --> 00:17:49.079
Xiaofang's right not to marry him.

00:17:49.500 --> 00:17:50.119
The baby,

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:51.299
We'll raise it ourselves.

00:17:51.660 --> 00:17:53.279
I raised the four of you,

00:17:53.519 --> 00:17:55.660
And none of you are missing limbs.

00:17:56.960 --> 00:17:57.599
What happened to you?

00:17:57.940 --> 00:17:58.660
It's nothing, nothing.

00:17:58.680 --> 00:17:59.240
Just took a fall.

00:17:59.319 --> 00:17:59.819
Let Mom see.

00:17:59.819 --> 00:18:00.500
It's fine.

00:18:00.619 --> 00:18:01.220
Come on, come on.

00:18:01.440 --> 00:18:02.480
Come with me to put medicine on it.

00:18:04.980 --> 00:18:05.359
Dad.

00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:06.759
Brother.

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:08.180
You're back just in time.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:09.700
Your daughter here,

00:18:09.700 --> 00:18:10.680
That whole loudspeaker thing,

00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:11.619
You heard it too, right?

00:18:12.140 --> 00:18:13.019
Give her a talking-to.

00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:17.660
I...

00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:20.500
What can I say?

00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:22.619
Your daughter refuses to marry,

00:18:23.019 --> 00:18:24.299
And you actually look pretty happy about it.

00:18:24.839 --> 00:18:25.279
Really?

00:18:28.279 --> 00:18:29.299
Aunt, here's the thing.

00:18:30.059 --> 00:18:32.200
Whether the shoe fits or not,

00:18:32.599 --> 00:18:33.680
Only the wearer knows best.

00:18:34.779 --> 00:18:35.839
So this matter, just...

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:37.359
Just let Xiaofang

00:18:40.779 --> 00:18:41.980
Decide for herself.

00:18:45.420 --> 00:18:46.119
Thanks, Dad.

00:18:46.740 --> 00:18:47.640
Why didn't you say so earlier?

00:18:48.680 --> 00:18:49.539
It's all up to her.

00:18:49.900 --> 00:18:51.339
Then why'd you call us back here?

00:18:52.299 --> 00:18:54.099
I skipped my Maldives trip

00:18:54.519 --> 00:18:55.859
To come back and worry about you all,

00:18:56.700 --> 00:18:57.480
And I'm not even welcome.

00:18:57.799 --> 00:18:58.359
Now I get it.

00:18:58.759 --> 00:19:00.099
I'm damned if I do,

00:19:00.279 --> 00:19:01.539
And damned if I don't.

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:02.940
You're fine, you're fine, you're fine.

00:19:03.299 --> 00:19:04.380
A good person, a good person.

00:19:05.259 --> 00:19:05.880
Aunt,

00:19:06.400 --> 00:19:07.460
You've worked so hard.

00:19:07.660 --> 00:19:08.039
How about this?

00:19:08.480 --> 00:19:09.680
I'll cook you a chicken

00:19:10.440 --> 00:19:10.839
To nourish you.

00:19:11.259 --> 00:19:11.799
No need.

00:19:12.440 --> 00:19:13.720
Save it for your daughter instead.

00:19:19.099 --> 00:19:20.180
Your Aunt

00:19:20.720 --> 00:19:21.500
Loves eating chicken.

00:19:39.859 --> 00:19:40.880
Aunt

00:19:41.559 --> 00:19:43.640
I know you love me the most

00:19:44.220 --> 00:19:45.259
If it weren't for you

00:19:45.400 --> 00:19:46.799
I'd still be all confused right now

00:19:49.940 --> 00:19:50.400
Fang'er

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:53.420
Ever since you were little

00:19:54.140 --> 00:19:55.779
You've grown up without a mother

00:19:57.500 --> 00:19:58.539
In my heart

00:19:59.019 --> 00:20:00.599
You're just like my own daughter

00:20:01.460 --> 00:20:02.279
So

00:20:02.720 --> 00:20:03.700
Everything I'm telling you

00:20:03.759 --> 00:20:05.059
Is truly for your own good

00:20:05.519 --> 00:20:08.299
Right now you think love matters most

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:10.299
But when you reach Aunt's age,

00:20:10.900 --> 00:20:12.079
You'll realize many things

00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:13.720
Are far more important than love

00:20:14.420 --> 00:20:15.559
Take right now, for example

00:20:16.460 --> 00:20:17.920
Having a child is the easy part

00:20:18.380 --> 00:20:19.980
Raising one is the hard part

00:20:20.319 --> 00:20:21.240
Once the baby's born

00:20:21.400 --> 00:20:22.400
What will you raise him with?

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:24.160
I've got some savings right now

00:20:24.279 --> 00:20:25.859
Enough for me and the baby for a while

00:20:26.140 --> 00:20:26.940
One illness

00:20:27.240 --> 00:20:28.240
Could wipe it all out

00:20:30.160 --> 00:20:30.980
Once I'm out of confinement

00:20:31.019 --> 00:20:32.079
I'll go find a job

00:20:32.220 --> 00:20:33.539
If I can't find work

00:20:33.759 --> 00:20:34.920
I'll do what Grandpa did

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:36.119
Go up the mountains to gather herbs

00:20:36.359 --> 00:20:37.200
Grandpa gathered herbs back then

00:20:37.220 --> 00:20:38.119
And supported a whole big family

00:20:38.140 --> 00:20:38.700
I can do it too

00:20:39.640 --> 00:20:40.759
Xiaofang

00:20:41.019 --> 00:20:41.720
Your grandpa's time was

00:20:41.759 --> 00:20:43.299
Decades ago

00:20:43.380 --> 00:20:44.599
Times have changed now

00:20:45.319 --> 00:20:47.079
You alone with a child in tow

00:20:47.559 --> 00:20:49.099
Being both father and mother

00:20:49.720 --> 00:20:50.599
In a few years

00:20:50.640 --> 00:20:51.839
You'll be worn out and haggard

00:20:52.480 --> 00:20:53.720
What decent man

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:54.980
Would still want you then?

00:20:57.940 --> 00:20:59.220
A man will come looking on his own

00:21:01.259 --> 00:21:01.759
Fanyan

00:21:03.019 --> 00:21:03.720
Which man?

00:21:04.299 --> 00:21:05.599
Must be a man here for you

00:21:06.359 --> 00:21:06.799
Fanyan

00:21:07.099 --> 00:21:07.599
Coming

00:21:13.599 --> 00:21:14.299
Old Miao

00:21:14.980 --> 00:21:15.940
You needed something from me?

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.759
My house is a total mess right now

00:21:17.799 --> 00:21:18.240
Hurry up and tell me

00:21:18.460 --> 00:21:19.500
Good news, good news!

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:20.519
Xiaofang

00:21:20.799 --> 00:21:22.220
Is it definite that she and the Qi family

00:21:22.359 --> 00:21:23.279
Aren't going any further?

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:25.940
How would I know?

00:21:26.240 --> 00:21:27.440
Those two young ones

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:28.880
They're just plain

00:21:29.019 --> 00:21:30.220
Lawless and reckless

00:21:30.359 --> 00:21:31.279
Okay, okay, okay

00:21:32.579 --> 00:21:33.960
Young Yao from town

00:21:34.140 --> 00:21:34.940
Do you remember him?

00:21:35.920 --> 00:21:37.519
There are plenty of Yaos in town

00:21:37.559 --> 00:21:38.380
How can I match every one

00:21:38.380 --> 00:21:39.480
Of them to a face?

00:21:40.019 --> 00:21:41.519
Yao Duohai's family

00:21:45.500 --> 00:21:45.980
Right, right, right

00:21:46.160 --> 00:21:47.900
They own the biggest pig farm

00:21:47.940 --> 00:21:48.319
That's right

00:21:49.420 --> 00:21:50.359
Young Yao

00:21:50.740 --> 00:21:52.220
Has taken a liking to your Xiaofang

00:21:53.539 --> 00:21:54.680
No way

00:21:54.819 --> 00:21:55.579
Don't believe it, huh?

00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:56.680
I didn't believe it either

00:21:57.220 --> 00:21:58.559
I asked around for ages

00:21:59.680 --> 00:22:00.579
This Young Yao

00:22:00.680 --> 00:22:01.480
Has eagerly

00:22:01.519 --> 00:22:02.960
Fallen for your Xiaofang

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:05.140
Well, well

00:22:06.380 --> 00:22:07.740
His family's pretty well-off

00:22:08.099 --> 00:22:08.640
Absolutely

00:22:08.940 --> 00:22:10.200
Go home and ask Xiaofang

00:22:11.140 --> 00:22:12.240
See if she's willing to meet him

00:22:12.559 --> 00:22:13.660
So I can arrange a time

00:22:14.099 --> 00:22:15.279
This little princess

00:22:15.279 --> 00:22:15.859
She'll meet him

00:22:27.660 --> 00:22:28.880
Model pig farmer

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:29.920
That's right

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:32.059
I've had some modest success

00:22:32.400 --> 00:22:33.940
Our pig farm here

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.240
Is the only one in town

00:22:35.279 --> 00:22:36.160
That's high-tech

00:22:36.539 --> 00:22:37.480
From the moment

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:38.160
A piglet is born

00:22:38.200 --> 00:22:39.559
Sensors monitor it automatically

00:22:39.660 --> 00:22:40.759
Feeding is precisely controlled

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:41.619
The entire process

00:22:41.880 --> 00:22:42.579
No manual labor

00:22:42.700 --> 00:22:43.420
All done by machines

00:22:44.019 --> 00:22:44.460
And over here

00:22:44.920 --> 00:22:45.420
We've also

00:22:45.460 --> 00:22:46.400
Specially introduced

00:22:46.440 --> 00:22:47.880
Piglet gender control technology

00:22:48.059 --> 00:22:49.460
Manual intervention, more boars

00:22:51.319 --> 00:22:51.940
Why?

00:22:52.359 --> 00:22:53.640
Because on the market

00:22:53.660 --> 00:22:54.480
Boars sell for 5,000 yuan more

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:55.339
Than sows

00:22:56.099 --> 00:22:57.420
But if nobody wants sows

00:22:57.460 --> 00:22:58.960
Who'll give birth to the boars?

00:22:59.799 --> 00:23:00.759
Sows can breed

00:23:01.240 --> 00:23:02.000
We just don't need so many

00:23:03.759 --> 00:23:04.579
I've always believed

00:23:04.660 --> 00:23:05.759
That running a business

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:07.160
Is like steering a ship

00:23:07.579 --> 00:23:09.240
On the vast, endless sea

00:23:09.880 --> 00:23:11.420
You must always control the direction

00:23:12.079 --> 00:23:12.759
Otherwise

00:23:12.900 --> 00:23:14.059
Once big storms hit

00:23:14.259 --> 00:23:15.180
You'll easily...

00:23:18.660 --> 00:23:19.299
Sorry

00:23:19.460 --> 00:23:19.900
I...

00:23:21.240 --> 00:23:24.140
Once I talk business, I can't stop

00:23:25.480 --> 00:23:26.480
Because of this

00:23:27.619 --> 00:23:28.680
Starting a family

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:29.680
Has been put off, you see

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:33.119
Come, have a seat

00:23:36.619 --> 00:23:39.299
I heard this is your first blind date.

00:23:39.900 --> 00:23:40.359
That's right.

00:23:41.240 --> 00:23:42.700
But I have to be honest with you.

00:23:42.720 --> 00:23:43.640
The reason I came on this date

00:23:43.720 --> 00:23:44.359
Is actually to

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:45.480
Push back against my Aunt.

00:23:45.819 --> 00:23:46.819
She keeps setting me up.

00:23:46.859 --> 00:23:47.880
I wanted to show her

00:23:47.920 --> 00:23:49.500
That I have plenty of options.

00:23:49.759 --> 00:23:51.119
I think you're absolutely right.

00:23:51.700 --> 00:23:52.319
Us young people,

00:23:52.339 --> 00:23:53.220
We've got tons of possibilities.

00:23:56.099 --> 00:23:57.339
Director Miao told me

00:23:57.380 --> 00:23:58.819
You picked me at first sight.

00:23:59.619 --> 00:24:00.039
Yeah.

00:24:00.579 --> 00:24:01.660
What do you like about me?

00:24:02.920 --> 00:24:04.559
I just like

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:05.839
Your straightforward personality.

00:24:06.220 --> 00:24:06.759
Xiaofang,

00:24:06.900 --> 00:24:08.339
Do you believe in intuition?

00:24:09.099 --> 00:24:09.460
I... I...

00:24:09.759 --> 00:24:11.119
When I first saw you,

00:24:13.200 --> 00:24:14.500
Just that one glance,

00:24:15.019 --> 00:24:16.500
One glance from afar.

00:24:19.500 --> 00:24:20.160
You hit me!

00:24:20.380 --> 00:24:21.400
That one's from him.

00:24:24.299 --> 00:24:25.160
And this one's from me.

00:24:26.220 --> 00:24:26.920
My heart

00:24:27.460 --> 00:24:28.160
Started to tremble

00:24:28.200 --> 00:24:29.220
With every step you took.

00:24:29.759 --> 00:24:30.779
With every step you took,

00:24:30.940 --> 00:24:32.380
My heart beat right along with it.

00:24:32.759 --> 00:24:33.519
When you walked away,

00:24:34.079 --> 00:24:35.319
You took my heart with you.

00:24:36.740 --> 00:24:38.279
Yao Jiahao, you're hilarious.

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:39.559
As for me,

00:24:39.599 --> 00:24:40.619
Besides running a business,

00:24:40.680 --> 00:24:41.900
I'm also quite the poetic soul.

00:24:43.079 --> 00:24:44.119
Yeah, I can tell.

00:24:44.200 --> 00:24:46.400
Who ties a bow on their stun baton?

00:24:47.039 --> 00:24:48.420
That's a memento.

00:24:48.859 --> 00:24:50.759
It commemorates my early pig-farming days.

00:24:51.039 --> 00:24:52.039
Back when I first started,

00:24:52.319 --> 00:24:53.519
If the pigs wouldn't behave,

00:24:53.799 --> 00:24:55.240
This thing worked like a charm.

00:24:59.380 --> 00:24:59.700
Okay.

00:25:00.220 --> 00:25:01.400
Bro, hurry, clean out the pigpen!

00:25:01.420 --> 00:25:02.160
The pigs are arriving!

00:25:02.460 --> 00:25:02.660
Okay.

00:25:02.700 --> 00:25:04.079
What? What pigs?

00:25:04.279 --> 00:25:04.480
Mom,

00:25:04.500 --> 00:25:05.420
We don't raise pigs.

00:25:05.740 --> 00:25:06.539
Who bought them?

00:25:07.160 --> 00:25:07.980
Nobody bought them.

00:25:08.740 --> 00:25:09.819
They're a gift.

00:25:10.420 --> 00:25:11.140
A gift?

00:25:11.200 --> 00:25:11.740
A gift.

00:25:12.099 --> 00:25:14.039
Whose sow just had piglets?

00:25:14.259 --> 00:25:15.680
We can't just take them for free.

00:25:16.700 --> 00:25:17.400
They're not piglets.

00:25:18.059 --> 00:25:18.819
It'll be here in a bit.

00:25:18.980 --> 00:25:20.200
It's a big boar.

00:25:21.119 --> 00:25:22.059
A big boar?

00:25:22.339 --> 00:25:23.019
They said it's almost here.

00:25:23.480 --> 00:25:24.299
Where is it?

00:25:40.859 --> 00:25:42.400
Hello, is this the Yang Xiaofang residence?

00:25:43.519 --> 00:25:45.039
You're the one who called me, right?

00:25:45.380 --> 00:25:46.200
Hello, hello, hello.

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:47.539
Our Boss Yao

00:25:47.559 --> 00:25:48.539
Asked me to deliver a pig

00:25:48.599 --> 00:25:49.339
To Yang Xiaofang's family

00:25:49.700 --> 00:25:50.440
As a token of thanks.

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:51.400
Thanks?

00:25:52.079 --> 00:25:52.759
What good deed

00:25:52.799 --> 00:25:54.339
Did our Xiaofang do?

00:25:54.779 --> 00:25:55.579
Yao Jiahao

00:25:55.740 --> 00:25:56.740
Is meeting Xiaofang for a matchmaking date.

00:25:56.960 --> 00:25:58.059
This is the first-meeting gift.

00:25:58.980 --> 00:25:59.559
Thank you!

00:26:00.640 --> 00:26:02.200
There's no room here for a truckload of pigs.

00:26:03.339 --> 00:26:03.839
Where's the pig?

00:26:03.880 --> 00:26:04.480
It's... not here.

00:26:05.059 --> 00:26:05.700
The pig is right here.

00:26:06.480 --> 00:26:06.980
Please keep it safe.

00:26:08.940 --> 00:26:09.299
This...

00:26:09.380 --> 00:26:10.480
This is a custom pig card.

00:26:11.059 --> 00:26:12.039
All pigs from our farm

00:26:12.279 --> 00:26:13.240
Are privately customized.

00:26:13.839 --> 00:26:15.119
