00:38:37.519 --> 00:38:38.019
Let me see.

00:38:38.559 --> 00:38:39.320
Oops, slippery fingers.

00:38:40.079 --> 00:38:41.420
Why are your hands so quick?

00:38:42.099 --> 00:38:44.019
What kind of comments are these?

00:38:44.119 --> 00:38:45.039
Filthy language.

00:38:45.260 --> 00:38:46.219
This just won't do.

00:38:46.699 --> 00:38:47.940
Those nasty comments...

00:38:47.940 --> 00:38:49.000
Just don't read them.

00:38:49.059 --> 00:38:49.639
Look here.

00:38:49.739 --> 00:38:51.019
So many people praising me!

00:38:51.400 --> 00:38:52.860
I didn't even know I was this great.

00:38:53.119 --> 00:38:53.699
Weren't you worried

00:38:53.739 --> 00:38:54.699
That I'd never get married?

00:38:55.280 --> 00:38:56.579
Look how many want to date me!

00:38:57.559 --> 00:38:57.960
Xiaofang.

00:38:59.119 --> 00:38:59.539
What?

00:39:00.780 --> 00:39:01.739
I just ran into the grandson

00:39:01.780 --> 00:39:03.000
Of Third Grand-Uncle from behind the hill.

00:39:03.480 --> 00:39:05.019
He insisted on shoving eggs into my hands.

00:39:05.239 --> 00:39:06.119
Said he wants to set up a date with you.

00:39:06.300 --> 00:39:07.199
Which Third Grand-Uncle?

00:39:07.619 --> 00:39:08.380
Which grandson?

00:39:09.019 --> 00:39:10.119
The one who works in the county town?

00:39:10.159 --> 00:39:10.860
That grandson?

00:39:11.039 --> 00:39:11.960
I don't know him well.

00:39:12.280 --> 00:39:13.139
But this guy,

00:39:13.179 --> 00:39:13.940
He's pretty good-looking.

00:39:14.199 --> 00:39:14.920
Do you want to meet him?

00:39:15.320 --> 00:39:16.280
Sure, set it up.

00:39:16.699 --> 00:39:18.380
But my schedule's pretty packed.

00:39:18.500 --> 00:39:19.199
By the time I'm free,

00:39:19.300 --> 00:39:20.400
I'll probably have already given birth.

00:39:20.619 --> 00:39:22.280
If you want to embarrass yourself even more,

00:39:22.400 --> 00:39:23.300
Just copy the neighbors across the way

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.579
And start live-streaming.

00:39:26.559 --> 00:39:27.159
Stop drinking.

00:39:28.420 --> 00:39:30.480
You and Xiaofang can't break up.

00:39:31.059 --> 00:39:32.820
There's a baby already. Break up? No way.

00:39:33.380 --> 00:39:34.440
It's just a little fight.

00:39:34.619 --> 00:39:35.659
A little disagreement.

00:39:36.139 --> 00:39:37.860
Women get over it once they vent.

00:39:38.099 --> 00:39:39.820
Isn't Xiaofang running that marriage ad?

00:39:41.039 --> 00:39:41.780
That's just...

00:39:42.599 --> 00:39:43.639
Her way of getting back at Xiaowei.

00:39:45.059 --> 00:39:46.239
It's trendy these days.

00:39:46.239 --> 00:39:47.260
Playing hard to get, you know?

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:49.380
Isn't that Qi Xiaowei?

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:50.400
Hey, your son...

00:39:50.400 --> 00:39:51.760
Is about to call someone else "Dad."

00:39:51.940 --> 00:39:53.159
And you're still in the mood to drink?

00:39:53.940 --> 00:39:55.019
You've got nerves of steel.

00:39:55.179 --> 00:39:55.920
I'm serious.

00:39:56.099 --> 00:39:57.820
Look at that artist's tolerance.

00:39:58.920 --> 00:39:59.800
Really something else.

00:40:00.639 --> 00:40:01.239
Xiaowei,

00:40:01.820 --> 00:40:03.400
You'd better win Xiaofang back fast.

00:40:03.820 --> 00:40:05.639
She's the belle of the village.

00:40:06.059 --> 00:40:08.119
Even Yao Jiahao's chasing after her.

00:40:08.260 --> 00:40:09.280
Now that she's put out a marriage ad,

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:10.400
So many guys are eyeing her.

00:40:10.639 --> 00:40:11.639
Getting a wife these days

00:40:11.739 --> 00:40:12.579
Is no easy thing.

00:40:13.199 --> 00:40:13.739
Just look at her.

00:40:13.739 --> 00:40:14.559
Xiaofang's looks...

00:40:14.760 --> 00:40:15.679
She's a real stunner.

00:40:16.519 --> 00:40:17.059
So pretty.

00:40:17.099 --> 00:40:17.940
No wonder they call her the village belle.

00:40:17.940 --> 00:40:18.539
I might try my luck too.

00:40:18.539 --> 00:40:20.019
If it actually works out with her,

00:40:21.039 --> 00:40:22.480
I'll be the real dad, you'll be the second dad...

00:40:22.760 --> 00:40:23.539
Figure out a title for yourself.

00:40:23.559 --> 00:40:24.300
I'll just be the godfather.

00:40:24.659 --> 00:40:25.219
Would that work?

00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:27.119
Speak up about this match, quick.

00:40:27.300 --> 00:40:28.340
I'll just go straight to godfather.

00:40:28.480 --> 00:40:29.559
Come on, cheers.

00:40:31.880 --> 00:40:32.679
Hey, what are you doing?

00:40:32.820 --> 00:40:33.780
Have you lost your mind?

00:40:34.920 --> 00:40:35.559
What the hell?

00:40:36.179 --> 00:40:37.119
Let go! Let go of me!

00:40:37.639 --> 00:40:38.139
What are you doing?

00:40:42.679 --> 00:40:43.960
What a piece of work.

00:40:44.099 --> 00:40:45.360
She'll do anything.

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:54.840
Stop right there.

00:40:55.639 --> 00:40:56.699
Don't you see your father?

00:40:57.380 --> 00:40:59.019
Who's that sour face for?

00:41:02.280 --> 00:41:03.039
I just lost my wife.

00:41:03.059 --> 00:41:04.219
And I still gotta smile for you?

00:41:04.800 --> 00:41:05.639
Wait, wait, hold on.

00:41:05.880 --> 00:41:06.440
Wait, wait, wait.

00:41:08.159 --> 00:41:08.800
What happened to your face?

00:41:09.639 --> 00:41:10.300
Did you get in a fight?

00:41:10.840 --> 00:41:11.920
Son, that took guts, real guts.

00:41:12.380 --> 00:41:13.099
Nice guts.

00:41:13.760 --> 00:41:14.260
Show those...

00:41:14.260 --> 00:41:15.420
Clueless punks a lesson.

00:41:15.860 --> 00:41:17.340
Anyone who gets tangled up with Yang Xiaofang...

00:41:17.420 --> 00:41:18.340
Sees how it ends up.

00:41:18.840 --> 00:41:19.539
How does it end up?

00:41:20.019 --> 00:41:20.719
Look at how I'm ending up.

00:41:20.739 --> 00:41:21.360
You tell me.

00:41:23.300 --> 00:41:24.440
Look at how pathetic you are.

00:41:24.719 --> 00:41:25.599
It's just Yang Xiaofang...

00:41:25.880 --> 00:41:26.800
Going on a blind date.

00:41:27.179 --> 00:41:28.099
If she wants to act up,

00:41:28.599 --> 00:41:29.679
Let her act up.

00:41:30.179 --> 00:41:31.019
Once nobody wants her,

00:41:31.320 --> 00:41:33.059
She'll come crawling back begging you to marry her.

00:41:33.320 --> 00:41:34.420
Then you'll have her wrapped around your finger.

00:41:34.760 --> 00:41:35.840
Wait, you're that confident?

00:41:37.659 --> 00:41:38.699
What if Yang Xiaofang...

00:41:38.719 --> 00:41:39.599
Marries someone else?

00:41:39.860 --> 00:41:41.039
What if she doesn't marry me?

00:41:41.480 --> 00:41:43.219
You keep saying nobody wants her.

00:41:43.340 --> 00:41:43.940
Have you ever considered...

00:41:43.940 --> 00:41:45.199
Whether anyone wants your son?

00:41:45.320 --> 00:41:46.139
My silly boy.

00:41:46.380 --> 00:41:48.079
That's absolutely impossible.

00:41:48.639 --> 00:41:49.340
After all, she's carrying...

00:41:49.380 --> 00:41:50.539
Your kid in her belly.

00:41:50.579 --> 00:41:52.239
What are you panicking about?

00:41:56.539 --> 00:41:56.940
Dad.

00:41:57.760 --> 00:41:58.760
Why did you marry my mom?

00:42:00.260 --> 00:42:01.219
Did you really love her?

00:42:01.920 --> 00:42:03.099
Do you even know what love is?

00:42:03.380 --> 00:42:04.719
Not everyone's like you.

00:42:04.760 --> 00:42:06.579
Money, money, money, that's all you care about.

00:42:06.900 --> 00:42:08.099
You've completely ruined my life.

00:42:08.139 --> 00:42:08.960
Are you happy now?

00:42:10.940 --> 00:42:12.039
That's bullshit!

00:42:12.860 --> 00:42:13.800
If I hadn't seen that you...

00:42:13.800 --> 00:42:15.119
Had a thing for that Yang Xiaofang,

00:42:15.739 --> 00:42:17.360
I'd have cut ties with the Yang family long ago.

00:42:20.059 --> 00:42:20.900
Yang Fanhu!

00:42:21.940 --> 00:42:23.019
You're just gonna let your daughter...

00:42:23.059 --> 00:42:24.099
Act like a lunatic?

00:42:24.739 --> 00:42:26.079
Aren't you ashamed?

00:42:47.239 --> 00:42:47.739
She's coming out!

00:42:47.739 --> 00:42:48.280
Is that her family?

00:42:48.360 --> 00:42:49.260
Am I still dreaming?

00:42:49.380 --> 00:42:50.019
Seriously?

00:42:51.280 --> 00:42:51.780
Is this our house

00:42:51.820 --> 00:42:53.059
Or a subway station at rush hour?

00:42:54.139 --> 00:42:54.480
She's out!

00:42:57.320 --> 00:42:57.860
Hello.

00:42:58.320 --> 00:42:59.579
Is this Yang Xiaofang's house?

00:43:01.480 --> 00:43:03.199
You're looking for Xiaofang?

00:43:03.639 --> 00:43:04.000
Yes.

00:43:04.119 --> 00:43:05.219
Bro, I came all the way from the county.

00:43:05.260 --> 00:43:06.400
Just to meet Xiaofang in person.

00:43:06.519 --> 00:43:08.539
Yeah, we just wanna meet Xiaofang.

00:43:09.260 --> 00:43:10.340
Are you here for a blind date?

00:43:10.460 --> 00:43:11.519
That's right.

00:43:11.699 --> 00:43:12.079
Xiaofang!

00:43:12.099 --> 00:43:13.219
Blind dates, they're all here for dates!

00:43:13.639 --> 00:43:14.039
Mom.

00:43:14.460 --> 00:43:15.039
Mom.

00:43:15.400 --> 00:43:15.820
Mom!

00:43:17.019 --> 00:43:18.840
Xiaofang blew the matchmaker's quota away!

00:43:18.840 --> 00:43:19.199
Mom.

00:43:23.480 --> 00:43:24.659
Are you wondering

00:43:25.059 --> 00:43:26.599
Why I'd even agree to date you?

00:43:26.820 --> 00:43:28.139
I really love kids.

00:43:28.460 --> 00:43:29.400
Let's have five or six.

00:43:29.699 --> 00:43:31.320
Five or six? Can you even afford them?

00:43:31.800 --> 00:43:33.159
I hope you'll wear more white from now on.

00:43:33.800 --> 00:43:34.559
It'll make you look

00:43:35.199 --> 00:43:35.739
Pure.

00:43:38.579 --> 00:43:40.219
Son, you better watch out.

00:43:40.260 --> 00:43:41.559
The more suitors she gets,

00:43:41.559 --> 00:43:43.219
The pickier she'll become.

00:43:43.800 --> 00:43:44.960
You've gotta do something.

00:43:45.239 --> 00:43:46.340
Sweet-talk her back home.

00:43:46.840 --> 00:43:48.460
It's time to end this farce.

00:43:49.079 --> 00:43:49.780
How do I end it?

00:43:50.760 --> 00:43:52.260
Bring out our secret stash.

